item.media:title: Rimuru Tempest :Food:
item.media:description:
I have been so dead on here lately, I have had zero inspiration but it has not stopped me from watching anime. I recently got into That time I got reincarnated as a slime and I have to say at first I wasn't hooked but I slowly fell in love with it. Honestly Rimuru is adorable and I just love the development of the characters throughout the show, I really do just love where it's going! 

Anyways this is some of my first piece of Fanart so I hope you enjoy~

Me and my mom have been visiting a nice, botanic garden in Hannover Cit.

They also got these greenhouses there in which you can find orchids and cacti and here you can see one of the latter.

Looks like a heart, doesn't it? A pretty dangerous heart

Your P.O.V

Goku and I are training until we both hear King Kai shout.

King Kai: NOOO!! THIS CAN'T BE!!

We stopped training and looked at King Kai.

Goku: Did something happen?

King Kai: B-B-Beerus h-he i-i-is c-c-coming.

'Who is Beerus and why is King Kai afraid of him.

Goku: Who is Beerus?

King Kai: Beerus is the God of Destruction!

'God of Destruction! Then that means he's strong!!'

Goku: Is he strong?

King Kai: Yes, and don't fight him Goku he is way out of your league!!

Goku: Seriously!! Now I'm more excited to fight him!

Y/N: Me too.
